{"tid":1141343,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奇異博士點解唔同人講架時光機會爆？","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T14:44:47.000Z","uid":114217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3b3f280b5ceaa39cbad8b3fbe2ca11c2c89867","tid":1141343,"uid":114217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"佢睇晒1/1400萬個未來<br />\n實知場大戰架時光機會爆<br />\n但佢睇住成班人戇鳩鳩輪流拎隻手套想去時光機都唔出聲，到底有咩居心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想IM死之後照顧佢老婆同個女？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8617416bfac8d23f9b8e20b526202182b22bd4fc","tid":1141343,"uid":113373,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n星期六 早上9點 <br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">事態危急</span><br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"029549a5561a3a25e85b8a6ce07ac84cf21e9013","tid":1141343,"uid":218659,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/05/06/200728_bf00eb56d589957eb4dfa5fc060edc62.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F05%2F06%2F200728_bf00eb56d589957eb4dfa5fc060edc62.gif&h=5802a2bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f83fc020b9c364febd1075f3d653ce6db0c5c307","tid":1141343,"uid":249170,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e3b3f280b5cea